4j. DHIS2 uses log4j2 directly via\nlog4j-slf4j-impl declared alongside spring-boot-starter-tomcat.\nHaving log4j-to-slf4j on the same classpath as log4j-slf4j-impl\ncrashes the executable WAR at startup with:\n\n  log4j-slf4j-impl cannot be present with log4j-to-slf4j\n\nExcluding spring-boot-starter-logging from spring-boot-starter-tomcat\nremoves the four unused-by-DHIS2 jars at the source. dhis.war can now\nbe run with `java -jar dhis-web-server/target/dhis.war` directly,\nmatching the procedure documented in AGENTS.md and run-api.sh.\n\nAI Assisted","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"},"id":"46bbf1cfdbb95b82c9eea5f80191dc935e87229b","tree_id":"766a1625ca2607234ab41507e5c40f23cbe25dcf","timestamp":"2026-05-02T19:09:06Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the serv